<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>潮汕牛肉丸，纯手工打制而成</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>坚持传统工序，手工现捏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每颗牛肉丸都经过“历练”，经验老道的师傅去除多余的筋膜和油脂后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201130/6605088570dd447c8e959a2b3b6c094e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201130/36b9358b8da4463bb4f699e421913c02.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">将一整锅粉红的牛丸高温熬煮上10几分钟，新鲜滚烫的牛丸就出炉啦。<strong>每天现打现做</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201130/b77d40e915054a2692a25380aa07bb45.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201130/b77d40e915054a2692a25380aa07bb45.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201130/c0a7d8db713941069a71ad4ef7b5ea08.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>4位丸子选手</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">【潮汕牛肉丸】主打牛肉丸和牛筋丸，<strong>颗颗超弹</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">●●●</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201130/82dd4f60c1f145478253dc4f1da9c500.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201130/e2778eed202c44feb5a2bd8963def63b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">Tips：牛肉丸会比较光滑细腻，口感爽口；而<strong>牛筋丸在牛肉丸基础上加入嫩筋</strong>，筋道多汁！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201130/22dc84428bfe40be9d440a5cb08b8c08.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">1</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">2</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">3</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201130/a5a19ae474484974a6ee9e22c7b4d642.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>牛肉丸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">纯牛肉打造的牛肉丸，<strong>表面比较光滑且均匀</strong>，个头圆鼓鼓很饱满，肉质细腻又嫩滑！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201130/83214d4f52834fa6b754d70e4b674f83.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>粒粒圆润饱满，紧实弹牙</strong>！小编还顽皮了一下，<strong>弹弹弹弹到飞起</strong>，这弹性度可以当乒乓球打啦！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201130/936583f7a0a9475cb206922fb80a2c8d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201130/936583f7a0a9475cb206922fb80a2c8d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">香浓的油脂在每个小气孔里冒出，<strong>不断迸发出汁水</strong>，飙飙飙飙汁场面停不下来，瞬间让人口水直咽！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201130/4ec1bcf00160423f8dc0dbcbeb0007e2.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201130/4ec1bcf00160423f8dc0dbcbeb0007e2.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201130/4ec1bcf00160423f8dc0dbcbeb0007e2.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201130/837a825b094f48ff90376ae9288cd8de.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">记得<strong>蘸上店家的特制蘸料开吃</strong>，口感依旧美味，还丝毫不影响牛丸的鲜香！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201130/f5d5854364d44942bdf1379555f36282.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>牛筋丸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这位牛筋丸选手也不甘示弱，口感韧劲筋道的它也同样抢手！加了嫩筋的牛筋丸，<strong>纤维更加紧致，更有嚼头</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201130/82c12a25ca71461a90f4b8ac052031fc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">煮熟后的牛筋丸圆鼓鼓的，撕开后还能看到<strong>内里肉质紧实丝丝相连</strong>，弹性十足</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201130/f97ca195ea1e4467aca327d8ca65d2fe.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201130/942bcc6f39274d7483797fe37b12c577.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>鳗鱼丸&amp;虾枣条</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">除了牛丸，店里还有<strong>自制的鳗鱼丸和虾枣条</strong>，口感依旧Q弹爽口！广东转凉啦，火锅局也要安排一下！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">●●●</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201130/a076a983717a45ae96ecee8b96fbdfaa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201130/53142310171542e489ca12b3d7b895f7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201130/c1ac879b9ecd40d59d619f270f14e751.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>花式牛丸做法，厨房小白也能GET</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>牛肉丸火锅</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">谁说牛肉丸只配麻辣锅底，搭配鲜蔬锅底才是完美的！简单鲜香的锅底才<strong>更突出牛肉丸的原汁原味</strong>。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201130/6a0aac5a78e2460b978e096d39cc7b45.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每颗牛肉丸吸收锅底的精华，<strong>紧紧锁住了鲜香</strong>，看着这咕噜咕噜的画面，肚子又开始饿了5555~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201130/9a3f719125ab474f88dd6c11322634b4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201130/4ee6d7ff9e094adbab5ad5baa2d5a523.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">待丸子一个个浮起来即可开吃，<strong>Q弹爽口的牛丸</strong>，<strong>一口就飙汁</strong>！干饭人，干饭魂，一口一个实在爽！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201130/957947e529654dee9a227839bc9def9a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>牛筋丸粿条</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">嘴馋想在家里吃上<strong>地道潮汕牛丸粿条</strong>，也不是问题，足不出户，轻松就能Get！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201130/c426c18ab7804b9cbef5e17bfccf2d9b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">先喝一口清汤，<strong>嗦一口粿条</strong>，<strong>再来一颗Q弹的牛丸</strong>，飘香四溢，带着微微的油脂香一点儿也不让人失望！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201130/a52b30b08a73494490c9ca15174a7775.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201130/a89167e8d7514929aa5bd83cf2097557.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>鳗鱼丸紫菜汤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">煮上一碗热腾腾的紫菜蛋花汤，搭配上<strong>爽口弹牙的鳗鱼丸</strong>，<strong>鲜香四溢</strong>，我还能喝上三碗！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201130/e95fb65839b44b3bb3347a6fdfc6818e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>爆炒虾枣条</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">家常小炒也得拥有姓名，<strong>将虾枣条切成片状</strong>，加入些许油、调料在热锅中，炒3分钟即可出锅！<strong>集鲜、香、咸多味</strong>，端上桌没多久就被抢光了~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201130/dc3ce4049eff43b2a4d64ba675ad662b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201130/4c3930a68963400f94baaafdc27c28c2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>真空包装，冷冻保鲜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">坚持健康0添加的原则，新鲜现做，一律<strong>采用真空保鲜包装配送</strong>！老板还超贴心，就<strong>连蘸料都给你配齐</strong>，打开直接开蘸！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201130/30ce7502f5d34a83abc5477057faf094.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">牛丸都会用泡沫箱和冰袋密封，到手还是冰凉冰凉的，丝毫不影响口感，让你可以在第一时间尝到经典的潮汕风味！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201130/e1731ed5ed3b46b3b5c6241f9e2526f2.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
